        "payload": "node.web.summary",
        "title": "Bridge Authoring Walkthrough",
        "purpose": "Bridges are how one graph safely imports or exports resources (node classes, edge classes, views, scripts, declarations). This walkthrough is about bridge nodes as a primitive, not about any one specific contract.",
